{"tid":1180962,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【明星代價】同靚靚出席晚宴被合照 張智霖︰吃了一頓不安樂茶飯","createTime":"2019-06-01T08:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T10:58:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"69ee598016d0955ad040c4c0a38342f831378861","tid":1180962,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"張智霖（Chilam）和太太袁詠儀（靚靚），經常夫妻檔上綜藝節目，有時更孖住出席一些商演或公開活動，他們出現都好受歡迎。近日二人結伴出席一個晚宴，並肩而坐，但他們未能安坐，因為晚宴上的賓客紛紛上前找二人「強行」合照。<br />\n其中一位內地網民在微博發帖貼了一張相，相中的靚靚被身旁一位男士集郵，同一時間在旁的Chilam同樣被身後另一班人正在集郵，拿住水杯的Chilam，表情有點趣怪，望住前方的鏡頭，這位網民還留言︰「智霖哥的表情太搞笑了，看到老婆跟別的男人拍照，眼瞪那麼大。」<br />\n難得的是Chilam轉發這網民的帖子，還留言︰「我喜歡這張照片，簡單，粗暴，站在你後面就必須合作合照，謝謝你們讓我吃了一頓不安樂茶飯，為我的減肥計劃又邁進一步。」連苗僑偉都在Chilam的帖子中留言︰「代價。」有網民回應說︰「做明星就是這樣啊。」<br />\n由於該網民獲Chilam轉發其帖子，本來是開心事，不過有不少網民留言指責他︰「明明就是在諷刺綁架合照的，讓人家連吃飯都吃不安樂。」引來網民一番討論，最後這位網民更將帖子刪走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190601/large/1559371598_1f4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190601%2Flarge%2F1559371598_1f4e.jpg&h=56560a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190601/large/1559371652_16b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190601%2Flarge%2F1559371652_16b6.jpg&h=3474ddfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190601/large/1559370396_89ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190601%2Flarge%2F1559370396_89ae.jpg&h=2bb5a4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190601/59665153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F59665153&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbbe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=96ba8a61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F59665153&h=65504dfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190601/59665153</a>"},{"pid":"3999569780908d9978132a4de3f047788e447f86","tid":1180962,"uid":90166,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"On9有錢收ga wor<br />\nd明星雞去陪老細食飯，又話自己冇安樂茶飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950c2c67df0f25e4f30558d1cbe5fab3bdd3954b","tid":1180962,"uid":208722,"like":3,"dislike":35,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"好想屌袁靚靚"},{"pid":"2d2051428a23c5171de00947a4ad7da0796cec8c","tid":1180962,"uid":130626,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"3999569780908d9978132a4de3f047788e447f86","tid":1180962,"uid":90166,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"On9有錢收ga wor<br />\nd明星雞去陪老細食飯，又話自己冇安樂茶飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"張智霖呢條友真係好冇腦"},{"pid":"7883444dca6f25bd395531101acea48f9b800ca4","tid":1180962,"uid":10715,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"你去晚宴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你話平時去餐廳食飯就話啫"},{"pid":"364484fb0227c4fb0243bb06263916d55f9f94eb","tid":1180962,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be837e3c87d5145a70f6ffdda988dd15114f423e","tid":1180962,"uid":73617,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"成個怨婦咁 唔怪得當年簽完澤東比人雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /